🎯 Strategy Concept:
This bot trades primary trend positions and automatically hedges when key support/resistance levels break, protecting your capital from reversals.
📊 Market Structure Detection:
Uptrend Structure:

✅ Higher Highs (HH): Each swing high is higher than the previous
✅ Higher Lows (HL): Each swing low is higher than the previous
🟢 Green triangles and lines

Downtrend Structure:

✅ Lower Highs (LH): Each swing high is lower than the previous
✅ Lower Lows (LL): Each swing low is lower than the previous
🔴 Red/Orange triangles and lines

💡 Trading Logic:
Primary Positions (Trend Following):
UPTREND:

Long Entry: Price breaks above Higher High

Opens 2x position size
Follows the trend
Green triangle marker



DOWNTREND:

Short Entry: Price breaks below Lower Low

Opens 2x position size
Follows the trend
Red triangle marker



Hedge Positions (Risk Protection):
When LONG (Uptrend):

Hedge Short: If price breaks below Higher Low (HL)

Support broken = potential reversal
Opens 1x SHORT position (hedge)
Orange X marker
Up to 2 hedge positions allowed



When SHORT (Downtrend):

Hedge Long: If price breaks above Lower High (LH)

Resistance broken = potential reversal
Opens 1x LONG position (hedge)
Aqua X marker
Up to 2 hedge positions allowed



🛡️ How Hedging Works:
Example Scenario:

Bot opens LONG (2x size) on Higher High break
Price pulls back and breaks Higher Low (support)
Bot opens HEDGE SHORT (1x size) automatically
Net Position: Still LONG 1x (2 - 1 = 1)
Protection: If trend reverses, hedge minimizes loss
If trend resumes: Close hedge, keep primary position

📈 Risk Management:
Stop Loss Options:

Fixed percentage-based (2% default)
Applied to all positions
Protects capital from major moves

Take Profit:

Fixed percentage (3% default)
Locks in profits automatically
Optional toggle

Position Sizing:

Primary: 50% equity (2x with pyramiding)
Hedge: 25% equity (1x)
Max 2 hedge positions per primary

🎨 Visual Features:
Swing Point Markers:

🔼 Triangles up: Swing lows (Green = HL, Red = LL)
🔽 Triangles down: Swing highs (Green = HH, Orange = LH)
Lines: Connect swing points showing structure

Support/Resistance Zones:

Red zones: Previous swing highs (resistance)
Green zones: Previous swing lows (support)
Automatically extend to right

Entry Signals:

🟢 Large green triangle: Primary long entry
🔴 Large red triangle: Primary short entry
🟠 Orange X: Hedge short entry
🔵 Aqua X: Hedge long entry

📊 Info Table Shows:

Market Structure: Uptrend ↑ / Downtrend ↓ / Neutral
Previous High/Low: Key levels being monitored
Primary Position: Current trend position
Hedge Count: How many hedges are active
Net Position: Actual market exposure
Open P&L: Real-time profit/loss
Performance Stats: Total trades, net profit

⚙️ Settings:
Swing Detection:

Length: 5 bars (adjustable 2-20)
Smaller = more swings, more signals
Larger = major swings only

Hedge Options:

Toggle hedge on/off
Auto-close hedges on retrace
Max number of hedges (1-3)

Risk Settings:

Stop loss percentage
Take profit percentage
Toggle each independently

🎯 Use Cases:
Best For:

Volatile markets with false breaks
Protecting trending positions
Risk-averse traders
Swing trading timeframes (15m - 4H)

Strategy Benefits:

✅ Automatic risk protection
✅ Reduces drawdown
✅ Captures reversals
✅ No manual intervention needed
✅ Clear visual feedback

This is a sophisticated hedging bot that automatically protects your positions while keeping you in profitable trends! 🚀
